headline.print_headline: Prosecutors in Jodi Arias Sentencing Retrial Deny Pornography Deleted
headline.main: Prosecutors in Jodi Arias Sentencing Retrial Deny Pornography Deleted

lead_paragraph: Arizona prosecutors on Wednesday denied claims by lawyers for convicted murderer Jodi Arias, who accused the state of deleting thousands of pornographic files from the victim's computer.
